  <summary date="2015-01-06T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Domestic Violence Safety Plan Grant Program Act of 2015 or My Sister's Keeper Act of 2015

 Directs the Attorney General to establish a program to award grants to eligible state and local governments, educational institutions, and non-profit organizations to develop, promote, and teach the importance of the critical role that can be played by relatives, friends, and co-workers in combatting domestic violence.</summary>
